    "Vehicle DetectionVehicle detection is one of the most basic and common tasks in various applications, such as traffic monitoring and intelligent driving.",
    "Vehicle detection is often the first choice when applying object detection techniques in a traffic environment.",
    "From traditional methods to modern deep-learning approaches, vehicle detection has undergone years of research and Development.",
    "However, due to the influence of various complex factors such as viewpoint changes, occlusions, and truncations, vehicle detection remains a challenging problem.",
    "These factors result in cars having different appearances and shapes in various situations, adding to the complexity of vehicle detection.Reference [39] improved the RPN network within the Faster R-CNN model framework."
  ],
